HEADWORD: Excruciation
<hw>Ex*cru`ci*a"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>excruciatio</ets>.]</ety> <def>The act of inflicting agonizing
pain, or the state of being thus afflicted; that which excruciates;
torture.</def> <rj><au>Feltham.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
